@Garlic Herb Butter{3.5%ounce}

Use and enjoy.

> Everything's better with butter. Garlic herb butter, to be specific! This rich
> and delicious accompaniment is guaranteed to make all your Father's Day food
> taste 100x better (scientific fact). Use to top your Surf & Turf Pack, make
> instant garlic bread, or simply stock up and keep in your fridge for an instant
> upgrade to any meal. (We especially love it for starting scrambled eggs or
> stirring into mashed potatoes.) You really can't go wrong.